Write-up for our first CircuitVerse assignment. 

Description of the assignment:
Based on the adder we did in class on Tues Aug 29, implement this in CircuitVerse -- (you MUST implement your solution in CV inside of the CV00 assignment.  Look in CV for your group membership.

After completing this -- take screenshots of the circuit showing that it works (iterate across all 4 different input combinations -- make sure you add textbox to CV schematic with your name, and student ID number and make sure that these are visible in the screenshots.

Then, take your work for the idea to truth table, to k-maps, to equations, to hand-written / drawn schematic, and include all of these in a WORD document (do not use PDF, etc) MUST BE WORD -- and submit all together as a single document in Moodle here.

